    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/588040/extras/0b94b01a3e24e73d37b8c72600812603.avif?t=1727165269\" width=616 height=616 /></span><br><i>用你的睿智和聪敏，帮助那些期盼着你的人们吧。</i><br><i>WILL：美好世界</i><br><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >阅读</h2></li></ul>你需要阅读每个游戏角色寄给你的书信，了解他们的烦恼，并解决他们的困惑。或许你不会与他们成为朋友，但请相信他们感激着你所做的一切。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/588040/extras/99c7a22e5ec529c83b38e0c562764638.avif?t=1727165269\" width=616 height=365 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >推理</h2></li></ul>故事的发生不是单纯的猜测，相信那句话“事出有因”。所以，做决定之前记得动脑哦，这才是改变命运的乐趣所在。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/588040/extras/a61e5421917a43baad4d81c8668aa7ae.avif?t=1727165269\" width=616 height=1179 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >发现</h2></li></ul>生活因为脑洞大开而美好，有时一些勇敢的尝试也会让你喜出望外。去创造和他们共同的回忆吧。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/588040/extras/e4badba96d25cda0057151f830662336.avif?t=1727165269\" width=573 height=493 /></span>",
